left class=m><span class=title> BREAKING NEWS:  Thicket Murder Spree Continues</span><hr size=1> Horrific Murder Spree Continues in the Vale, Leatherfoot Raider patrols doubled in the Thicket!<br>
Senior Agent Mumsley Thunderfoot Reporting<br>
<br>
Sugarfoot Deeppockets has gone missing!<br>
<br>
It was said she was taking her usual early morning stroll through the Misty Thicket with her close friend Gingerhopp Diggs, when Sugarfoot, daughter of the honorable Mac Deeppockets, was attacked by a fierce troll....right in our very own Misty Thicket!<br>
<br>
Gingerhopp fainted dead away at the sight of the horrible troll, who snatched up the screaming, kicking, Sugarfoot and vanished.  Sugarfoot's current fate is unknown, however with an assailant with dietary habits such as trolls are known to have there is very little hope that she is still alive.<br>
<br>
Young Sugarfoot was a prominant member of the Rivervale Catillion, North End Chapter, chairperson for the Young Coalition for the Embetterment of Bixie Relations, and the youngest member ever of the North End Back-Stitch Needlepoint and Embroidery Circle.  Her friends recall her as a sweet caring young halfling who had impeccable grace and manners.  She is the daughter of Mac Deeppockets, a prominent member of one of the Vale's most influential and respected families.<br>
<br>
Mayor Gubbins had the following to say regarding the incident:  &quot;This is a terrible terrible tragedy.  Sugarfoot was beloved by all and her father is simply heartbroken.  Happy hour on Wednesday nights in the Fool's Gold will never be the same in the Vale again!  Even Lendel's Grand Lager will never taste the same.  I, your duly elected mayor and representative of the fine people of the Vale, swear that by any and all means the killer will be brought to justice!&quot;  After this he became tearstricken and could not continue.<br>
<br>
Gingerhopp has yet to recover from a severe onset of shock and is under the constant watch of friends and family as Priestess Hendi Mrubble nurses her back to health.  From her mutterings while in shock, we have thus far been able to determine that the attacker was a troll, but no further information has been obtained.  When Gingerhopp recovers she will be interviewed to discover more details about her attacker.  A followup report will be issued as soon as the information is received<br>
<br>
This incident is the latest occurance in a string of mysterious vanishings, bringing the total number of disappearances to four halflings that have now vanished during the course of the last month.  The motives of the assailant have yet to be determined.<br>
<br>
Sherrif Roglio has temporarily doubled the number of patrolling Marshals in the Thicket until the attacker is found and has assigned Marshal Anrey to organize the full resources of the elite Leatherfoot Raiders toward the ending of these murders.  Several agents have been recalled from the field to assist in scouring the Vale.<br>
<br>
If any halfling should provide key information or assistance leading to the apprehension of the assailant, a reward has been offered such that they will be immediately granted honorary membership in the Leatherfoot Raiders and receive the much prized Leatherfoot Raider Skullcap.  Mumsley Thunderfoot has been appointed the director of public relations in this important matter and will serve as the point of contact for all public inquiries and reports.<br>
<br>
