<br>
It seems the goblins of the Citadel are planning an attack on the vale and are running short on funds.<br>
<br>
The mention of a Troll was not discussed but you may want to start inquiring the Goblins of the Citadel for information leading to her kidnapping and return. I do hope she is alright, as I am familiar, being a Wood Elf, with the Trolls eating habits.<br>
<br>
I do hope this will help in the safe return of young Sugarfoot and bring her captures to justice.<br>
<br>
If a hunting party is to be formed to capture and question the goblins of the Citadel please let me know for I would be willing to assist in this valiant effort. <p><FONT SIZE="+1">Be Safe!  Have Fun! No Dying!</FONT><BR>
